“I know I’ll be sleeping soundly thanks to the Owlet Monitor Duo. I can track his oxygen level and heart rate in real time through the Owlet App and the award winning Smart Sock will notify us if his readings fall out of a preset zone, giving us the comfort we need to get a good night’s rest.”

"Pippa is always SO happy when she first wakes up! So when I see that she is awake through our @owletcare Cam, I come running. I love the Owlet Smart Sock, but honestly their Cam is just as amazing - it has two-way audio, sound and motion notifications (my fave), and 1080p with night vision. You don’t need the Smart Sock to have the Cam and it’s so easy to use through their app!" - @haileydevine

We all deserve a wake up call as cute as this! 🥰

Follow the link in our bio to shop the Cam and other award-winning Owlet monitors.

It’s Baby Safety Month and we’re sharing our favorite tips to ensure your little one’s sleep space is as safe as possible. 

Swipe through to see the simple steps to remember when you lay your baby down for their nap or bedtime. 💤 Follow the link in our stories for a post full of tips for making your baby’s nursery safer.

Share these tips with a friend who might find them useful!
